-- Shares of Turkey's Bank Asya slump 11 percent at open
-- 
-- Thu Sep 18, 2014 02:42AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Sept 18 (Reuters) - Shares in Turkey's Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS>, an Islamic finance institution, slumped 11 percent at the opening to 0.57 lira ($0.26) on Thursday, falling the maximum amount allowed in a single session for the fourth consecutive day.

